definition.value: A quinolone that is 1,2-dihydroquinoline substituted by an oxo group at position 2.
An organic chloride salt of thiamine(1+) diphosphate.
An oxo monocarboxylic acid that is (3-oxocyclopentyl)acetic acid substituted by a (2Z)-pent-2-en-1-yl group at position 2 of the cyclopentane ring.
